zofu
------------------------------------------
Zofu (Zofu is Object-oriented Fortran Unit-testing) is a framework for carrying
out unit testing of Fortran code modules. As the name suggests, it makes use of
the object-oriented features of Fortran 2003.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.1.7-1
  libgfortran5-10.2.0-1
  libopenmpifh40-3.1.6-1
  libzofu-devel-1.0.0-1bl1
  libzofu0-1.0.0-1bl1
  pkg-config-1.6.3-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.34+1git.de9c1b7cfe-1
  cygport-0.34.0-1
  gcc-core-10.2.0-1
  gcc-fortran-10.2.0-1
  meson-0.54.3-1
  ninja-1.10.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/acroucher/zofu

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/acroucher/zofu/archive/v1.0.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack zofu-1.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./zofu-1.0.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/zofu-1.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/zofu-1.0.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libzofu0-1.0.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libzofu-devel-1.0.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(zofu)
  /usr/bin/zofu-driver.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/zofu.README
  /usr/share/doc/zofu/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/zofu/README.md

(libzofu0)
  /usr/bin/cygzofu-0.dll

(libzofu-devel)
  /usr/include/zofu.mod
  /usr/include/zofu_kinds.mod
  /usr/include/zofu_mpi.mod
  /usr/include/zofu_scan.mod
  /usr/include/zofu_str_utils.mod
  /usr/lib/libzofu.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/zofu.pc

